        <tr>
      <th>Identity file</th>
      <td>
        <input type="text" id="settings_rjc_identity_file" 
                           value="<%= settings['rjc_identity_file'] %>" 
                           name="settings[rjc_identity_file]" >
                 </td><td>
                           The private key file for Jenkins CLI authentication, it is used only for executing CLI commands.
                           Also remember to upload the public key to &lt;Server IP&gt;:&lt;Server Port&gt;/user/&lt;Username&gt;/configure. 
                           Using this will override username/password settings.

      </td>
    </tr>
    
